I"c<p>This short MySQL script shows an aproach to compute the moving average.</p>

<h4 id="mysql---7-day-moving-average">MySQL - 7 Day Moving Average</h4>

<pre><code class="language-SQL">      SELECT 
      FROM signups
      JOIN signups as sigups_past 
      ON signups_past.date between signup.date - 6 and signups.date
      GROUP BY 1, 2
</code></pre>
